<paragraph id="IFRS16_68" base="F45929493"><paranum>68</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRSÂ 16"/><data name="paranum" value="68"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS16_P0254">The <xref base="F45929747" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0382">lessor<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0222"/></ph></xref> shall use the <xref base="F45929676" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0362">interest rate implicit in the lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0195"/></ph></xref> to measure the <xref base="F45929758" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0383">net investment in the lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0256"/></ph></xref>. In the case of a <xref base="F45929841" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0391">sublease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0359"/></ph></xref>, if the interest rate implicit in the sublease cannot be readily determined, an intermediate lessor may use the discount rate used for the head <xref base="F45929685" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0363">lease<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0214"/></ph></xref> (adjusted for any <xref base="F45929669" href="IFRS16_APPA.dita#IFRS16_APPA/IFRS16_P0360">initial direct costs<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0182"/></ph></xref> associated with the sublease) to measure the net investment in the sublease.</p></body></paragraph>